                        <h5>How Much Will My Shipment Cost?</h5>
                    </button>
                </h1>
                <div id="item1" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">Shipping cost depends on origin, destination, service, package weight, and other considerations such as pickup.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item text-light" style="background-color: #042967">
                <h1 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#item2" style="background-color: #042967">
                        <h5>How Should I Pack My Shipment?</h5>
                    </button>
                </h1>
                <div id="item2" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Use a rigid box with flaps intact</li>
                            <li>Remove any labels, hazardous materials indicators, and other previous shipment markings on the box that are no longer applicable</li>
                            <li>Wrap all items separately</li>
                            <li>Use adequate cushioning material</li>
                            <li>Use strong tape designed for shipping</li>
                            <li>Do not use string or paper over-wrap</li>
                            <li>Use a single address label that has clear, complete delivery and return information</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item text-light" style="background-color: #042967">
                <h1 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#item3" style="background-color: #042967">
                        <h5>I’ve Forgotten My Username and/or Password, or They No Longer Work. What Should I Do?</h5>
                    </button>
                </h1>
                <div id="item3" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Select "Forgot Password?" at the bottom of the login dropdown. This takes you to the “Reset or recover your login” settings screen. <br />

                        Enter your registered username to rerive your passowrd via email. If you for got your username enter your registered Email Address and we’ll send you an email to reset your username.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item text-light" style="background-color: #042967">
                <h1 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#item4" style="background-color: #042967">
                        <h5>The Status Of My Shipment Is “Out for Delivery.” When Will I Receive My Package?</h5>
                    </button>
                </h1>
                <div id="item4" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Typically, our drivers are on a 12 hour shift to provide a convenient 24/7 deliverly drop off, but most likely most packages deliver as late as 8 p.m. If we are unable to deliver a package that shows a status of "out for delivery," we will attempt delivery on the next business day.
                        <br />
                        Please note that we are unable to contact our drivers to provide an estimated delivery time.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item text-light" style="background-color: #042967">
                <h1 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#item5" style="background-color: #042967">
