                    </button>
                </h1>
                <div id="item5" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        If you are a reciver, look for tracking details indicating a problem with the address, look for the "Correct Reciver's Address" button. If this button does not appear, please contact the sender to note the error in the address. The sender should correct the address and pass the updated information to UPS.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
